Privacy Policy for LoopFurElise

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

At LoopFurElise, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information that we collect and how we use it.

1. Information We Collect
LoopFurElise does not collect any personal data from users. We do not require users to create an account, submit personal information, or engage in any actions that involve the collection of personal data.

2. Usage Data
The app does not track or collect usage data related to your interactions with the app. It simply plays an audio file in a loop and displays animations.

3. Third-Party Services
LoopFurElise does not use third-party services such as analytics, advertising networks, or social media integrations. As a result, no data is shared with third-party providers.

4. Data Storage
Since LoopFurElise does not collect or store any personal data, there is no user data stored on our servers or any other remote servers. Any data used within the app (such as audio files) is stored locally on your device.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make changes, we will update the "Effective Date" at the top of this page. We encourage users to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: [Insert your contact email]

